import React from 'react'
import './assets/css/base/base.css'
import { BrowserRouter, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './paginas/Home'
import Sobre from './paginas/Sobre'

function App() {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Route exact path='/'>

      <Home />

    </Route>
      
      <Route path='/sobre'>

      <Sobre />

      </Route>

    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
